## ðŸ”µ Blue Pill â€” *Just Get Me Started*

If your goal is to **start coding as quickly as possible**, this is the recommended path.

### Why we using platform IO for Blue Pill path !?

- Initial setup with the **Arduino IDE** was unreliable
- Using AI tools (e.g. Copilot) inside Arduino IDE felt limiting

Thats why we used **PlatformIO** instead of **Arduino-IDE**.



### âœ… Quick Start Checklist

- [ ] Install **Visual Studio Code**
- [ ] Install the **PlatformIO** extension
- [ ] Install squareLine Studio 1.4.0
- [ ] Open the provided **template project**
- [ ] Start developing immediately



